These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, accountant
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, skateboarding
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the engineer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | board-games       | filmmaking |
| Job         | accountant | engineer  |
| Sport       | skateboarding    | swimming    |
| Transport   | snowmobile       | bus      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, police-officer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, sports
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, golf
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the writer is on the far left##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Job           | writer | police-officer      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | animation      |
| Sport         | climbing | golf     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, eggplant
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, blues
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | coffee | lemonade  |
| Food          | grapefruit    | eggplant   |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | house   |
| Transport     | scooter     | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
There 2 different types of food: lime, pepper
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, fisherman
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, ambient
1. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
2. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking tea is the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | milk       | tea |
| Food          | pepper         | lime    |
| Job           | fisherman | electrician    |
| Music-Genre   | funk           | ambient   |

