2 different pets are kept: rat, goat
1. the indonesian is the owner of the goat##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | nectarine | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | hip-hop      |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    |
| Pet           | rat    | goat    |

