.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, paramedic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, documentary
2 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, roller
1. the social-worker is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the social-worker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the cat is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | paramedic | social-worker     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama          | documentary |
| Pet           | cat          | guinea-pig    |
| Transport     | roller            | helicopter       |

 